body.name: COSORI Dual Basket Air Fryer 9 Qt, Large and Wider Double Airfryer, 8-in-1, Sync Cook & Finish Family Meals, Bake, Roast, Broil and Dehydrate, Optional Preheat & Shake, Visible Window, 130 Recipes
deliveryMessages: Or fastest delivery Thursday, February 15. Order within 3 hrs 8 mins
features: Two Visual Baskets with Independent Panels: The design of independent operation panels and visual cooking process make it easier for you to monitor and complete two cooking projects, whether you're preparing juicy meats or nutritious side dishes at the same time.
6-in-1 Versatile Cooking Functions: Air Fry, Air Broil, Roast, Bake, Reheat, and Dehydrate, with customizable preheat and shake features, adding a touch of personalization to your cooking routine.

SyncCook: Master Two Dishes at Once: Cook a juicy steak in one basket and crispy fries in the other, all with the same settings: two baskets will cook with the same time, temperature, Preheat, and shake reminder settings.

SyncFinish: No More Waiting!: This smart setting ensures both baskets finish cooking together, even if your dishes have different times. Ensuring a complete meal, piping hot and ready, without the juggling act.
Abundant Cooking Space: Featuring an impressive 9.0Qt capacity with two independent 4.5Qt cooking zones, this Dual Basket Air Fryer is your gateway to simultaneous, diverse culinary creations.
Healthy Delights: Enjoy 85% less oil for healthier meals. Dual basket cooking prevents ingredient contamination, catering to special dietary needs.

130+ Recipes: With Cosori's 30 cookbook and 100 online recipes, you'll have everything you need to become a cooking pro. The recipes are easy to follow and the VeSync app provides helpful tips and tricks along the way.
Dishwasher-Safe Convenience: With two nonstick BPA-free baskets, making your cooking experience hassle-free.

SPECIFICATIONS: This Air Fryer is ETL-Listed with a power rating of 120V / 1750W, a wide temperature range (95-450℉) , and a 1-60 minute timer for accurate cooking. Please note that this voltage only applies to the US and Canada.
CALIFORNIA ROOTS: Based in California, COSORI is proud to call the Golden State our home.
body.description: Elevate your culinary journey with COSORI Dual Basket 9.0 Quart Air Fryer Unleash the power of double baskets, and embark on a culinary adventure that transforms every meal into a masterpiece. Visible Windows provide a front-row seat to perfection, ensuring every bite is a delight.With 6 cooking functions, preheat, and shake control at your fingertips, the Dual Basket Air Fryer puts precision in your hands. SyncCook & SyncFinish for simultaneous feasts. Whether it's healthy treats or a gourmet meal, the possibilities are endless. Specifications:Model: CAF-R901-KUSCapacity: 9.0 QtTemp Range: 95°F–450°FTime Range: 0-48 hourSingle Basket Dimensions(D x W x H): 6.9 x 18.5 x 4.5 inProduct Dimensions(D x W x H): 15.4 x 17.3 x 11.9 inWeight: 20 lb / 9.0 kgRated Power: 1750WPower Supply: AC 120V, 60HzTest Run:In order to make sure the air fryer is working correctly and remove potential odors from the manufacturing process, please follow the instructions in the manual for the Test Run before cooking with your air fryer.
